## Skyscraper Config

in `~/.skyscraper/config.ini` put the following

``` conf
[main]
frontend=pegasus
unattend=true
relativePaths=true
lang=en
region=us

[snes]
inputFolder=/home/savolla/resource/games/games/snes
gameListFolder=/home/savolla/resource/games/games/snes
mediaFolder=/home/savolla/resource/games/games/snes/media
emulator=retroarch -L /home/savolla/.config/retroarch/cores/snes9x_libretro.so

